snippet.title: eFootball™2023 Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to eFootball™ 2023!

We have added New licences and cards, as well as more variety, including "eFootball™ Coins" as rewards for events.

You can read about all the new features and adjustments we have made based on your feedback in the patch notes:
https://www.konami.com/efootball/ 

We hope you enjoy eFootball™ 2023 with the new season data.

#eFootball #FreeToPlay
